<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub20338702_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="剧情简介" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">美味奇缘</span>剧情简介</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">西餐明星主厨李雨哲<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8A%AB%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E5%B0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E8%A3%B4%E5%96%84%E5%AE%98"><i>披拉·尼迪裴善官</i></a><i>饰）</i>与电视美食节目小编导<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="角色海报"  href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/20714678/0d338744ebf81a4ceb865329df2a6059242da69e?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:147px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:145px;height:220px;">
<img class="picture" alt="角色海报" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=a5b963f4b099a9013f355c342d940a58/0d338744ebf81a4ceb865329df2a6059242da69e.jpg" style="width:145px;height:220px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
角色海报<span class="number">(8张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:139px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:133px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
宋佳茗<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AF%9B%E6%99%93%E5%BD%A4"><i>毛晓彤</i></a><i>饰）</i>因为制作节目而相识，李雨哲痴迷美食，有着从法国蓝带厨艺学院毕业的光鲜背景，自营的餐厅格调高雅。宋佳茗天生味觉极佳，协助父亲宋德忠<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%94%B0%E9%9B%A8/17588" data-lemmaid="17588"><i>田雨</i></a><i>饰）</i>经营着一家人气很旺的传统小吃店。为了制作节目，宋佳茗与冷面厨神李雨哲在理念上产生了种种冲突，但是经过磨合，雨哲被佳茗对料理的天赋与热爱所打动，也逐渐被佳茗个性中的明朗和坚韧所吸引，佳茗也逐渐感受到雨哲冷漠面孔下的真实与魅力，两人从最初的欢喜冤家到逐渐被对方所吸引，然而上一辈千丝万缕的恩怨纠葛却令他们备受考验，两人历经坎坷却依旧坚持梦想勇往直前 。另一方面，叶以澜<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%99%88%E6%AC%A3%E4%BA%88"><i>陈欣予</i></a><i>饰）</i>、李雨哲、赵寒<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%A0%E9%9B%A8%E5%89%91"><i>张雨剑</i></a><i>饰）</i>是一起长大的好伙伴，雨哲对佳茗的感情令以澜心生嫉妒，以澜不顾暗恋自己的赵寒，刻意接近和追求雨哲。与此同时，宋家小吃店所在的老洋房又面临被蓄意收购，佳茗的家庭和爱情都遭遇了危机，但是她意外发现自己苦寻多年的母亲陈丽华<i>（杨雪饰）</i>，竟然是以澜的继母。以澜的弟弟以轩<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B9%E9%80%B8%E4%BC%A6"><i>方逸伦</i></a><i>饰）</i>，跟雨哲的妹妹雨曦<i>（</i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9B%9B%E6%9C%97%E7%86%99"><i>盛朗熙</i></a><i>饰）</i>因创业相识，两人在偷偷相恋。几个年轻人背后千丝万缕的联系和秘密，随着年轻人之间的情感纠葛和事业竞争一点点被揭开。<sup>[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_20338702">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub20338702_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="分集剧情" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">美味奇缘</span>分集剧情</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
