<a name="角色介绍" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">美味奇缘</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/aa18972bd40735fa02f98f7794510fb30e2408f7?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D87%2C158%2C1303%2C1847%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=cc0cebcee324b899ca732378533e2ab9/aa18972bd40735fa02f98f7794510fb30e2408f7.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%A8%E5%93%B2">李雨哲</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/Mike/13013936" data-lemmaid="13013936">Mike</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
西餐厅明星主厨，性格高冷，用情专一，完美主义者，痴迷于美食，尤其在美食方面上的要求让人无法忍受。因制作一档美食节目与宋佳茗不打不相识，两人从最初的欢喜冤家到逐渐被对方所吸引，然而上一辈千丝万缕的恩怨纠葛却令他们备受考验，两人历经坎坷却依旧坚持梦想勇往直前，但雨哲因为坚持梦想与父亲的规划背道而驰。<div><div></div></div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/fc1f4134970a304e9d366134dbc8a786c8175cec?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D103%2C142%2C1303%2C1847%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=c8e6cf39953df8dcb272d5d1f02042b8/fc1f4134970a304e9d366134dbc8a786c8175cec.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%8B%E4%BD%B3%E8%8C%97">宋佳茗</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AF%9B%E6%99%93%E5%BD%A4">毛晓彤</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
电视台美食节目的编导，味觉灵敏，性格开朗，坚持梦想，不畏前行，认准了目标就会一直努力向前。每天乐观的她拥有一段忧伤的故事。无论是多舛的身世还是坎坷的爱情，都不能将她轻易击败。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/203fb80e7bec54e7b47bdbd0b3389b504ec26a6d?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D95%2C134%2C1287%2C1832%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=c39e63f43a4e251ff6b8beb89abffc3b/203fb80e7bec54e7b47bdbd0b3389b504ec26a6d.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B5%B5%E5%AF%92/22159300" data-lemmaid="22159300">赵寒</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%A0%E9%9B%A8%E5%89%91">张雨剑</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
美食节目负责人，精英暖男，是一个给人带来温暖的人，对下属宋佳茗百般呵护，虽然外表温暖，内心实则饱受仇恨的折磨。为了一个念想默默守候着叶以澜，多次尝试告白却都被叶以澜回绝，后与李雨哲反目。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/e824b899a9014c084eb4e96b007b02087af4f475?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D71%2C166%2C1303%2C1847%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=71bd2d07dd2a6059465fbb5a150305b7/e824b899a9014c084eb4e96b007b02087af4f475.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8F%B6%E4%BB%A5%E6%BE%9C">叶以澜</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%99%88%E6%AC%A3%E4%BA%88">陈欣予</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
与李雨哲是青梅竹马，富家千金，在职场中干练利落，但遇到爱情却变得敏感脆弱，兢兢战战，喜欢李雨哲，为了爱情可以不折手段。面对李雨哲，她放弃骄傲选择疯狂而卑微地追逐爱情，最终却使自己堕入深渊。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/b58f8c5494eef01f8783e0e1ebfe9925bc317d7b?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D79%2C166%2C1295%2C1839%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=606e9cce8acb39dbd58f3d16ed213008/b58f8c5494eef01f8783e0e1ebfe9925bc317d7b.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8F%B6%E4%BB%A5%E8%BD%A9">叶以轩</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B9%E9%80%B8%E4%BC%A6">方逸伦</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
叶以澜的同父异母的弟弟，公子哥，因长辈的关系，一向不受重视，玩世不恭，事业处处受挫，左冲右突中不断成长的富三。被父母“欺管严”，生活因奶奶变得囧连不断。泡妞借车、还得变身包租公催收房租，成为最囧富三代代言人。在遇到心爱的女人，经历了一番苦难后，成为了一个有担当的人。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E7%BE%8E%E5%91%B3%E5%A5%87%E7%BC%98/19690849/0/35a85edf8db1cb138caec6f6d654564e93584b14?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C242%2C341%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=6c8df6c7b81bb0519b6be9680b4af684/35a85edf8db1cb138caec6f6d654564e93584b14.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
李雨曦
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9B%9B%E6%9C%97%E7%86%99">盛朗熙</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
李雨哲的妹妹，职业为设计师，虽然是千金小姐，但却没有有钱人的那种势力。开朗活泼，鬼马精灵，心地善良，与叶以轩偷偷相恋。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="expand-all-container">
